# Cline's Learning Journal

## Project Conventions

- Using .NET Aspire for cloud-native development
- Implementing Google authentication for user access
- Using Azure SQL Database for data persistence
- Using target-typed new expressions (e.g., `List<string> items = new()`)

## Implementation Notes

- Enhanced expense model to support various splitting scenarios and currency tracking
